## MODULE DEPENDENCY FLOW

```
CLI/GUI → InteractiveBackend → IterationExecutor → Pipeline → Stages → Agents → Tools → LLM/Persistence
```

## KEY TRAIT DEFINITIONS

### InteractiveBackend
- Location: `crates/cowork-core/src/interaction/mod.rs`
- Purpose: Abstraction for CLI/GUI interaction
- Implementations:
  - `CliBackend`: `crates/cowork-core/src/interaction/cli.rs`
  - `TauriBackend`: `crates/cowork-core/src/interaction/tauri.rs`

### Stage
- Location: `crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/mod.rs`
- Purpose: Define stage execution behavior
- Implementations: `crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/stages/*.rs`

## CRITICAL CALL CHAINS

### 1. Create and Execute Genesis Iteration

```
User Request (CLI/GUI)
    │
    ▼
IterationExecutor::create_genesis_iteration()
    │ Location: crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/executor/mod.rs:35
    │ Creates Iteration with status=Draft
    │ Saves to IterationStore
    ▼
IterationExecutor::execute()
    │ Location: crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/executor/mod.rs:72
    │ Loads iteration, prepares workspace
    │ Determines start stage (idea for genesis)
    ▼
execute_stages_from()
    │ Location: crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/executor/mod.rs:138
    │ Iterates through stages
    │ For each stage:
    ▼
Stage::execute()
    │ Location: crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/stages/*.rs
    │ Creates Agent, executes with tools
    ▼
StageResult::Success or StageResult::Failed
    │ If Success and critical stage:
    ▼
InteractiveBackend::request_input()
    │ HITL confirmation gate
    │ Returns: Continue / ProvideFeedback / Cancel
    ▼
[If feedback provided]
Stage::execute_with_feedback()
    │ Re-runs stage with feedback context
```

### 2. Actor-Critic Loop (PRD/Design/Plan/Coding Stages)

```
Stage::execute()
    │
    ▼
StageExecutor::execute_stage()
    │ Location: crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/stage_executor.rs
    │
    ▼
create_*_loop_with_id() (e.g., create_prd_loop_with_id)
    │ Location: crates/cowork-core/src/agents/mod.rs
    │ Creates LoopAgent with [Actor, Critic]
    │ max_iterations = 1 (to avoid SequentialAgent bug)
    ▼
LoopAgent::run()
    │ Executes Actor → Critic sequence
    │
    ├─► Actor: Uses tools (LoadIdeaTool, SavePrdDocTool, etc.)
    │          Generates artifact
    │
    └─► Critic: Uses tools (GetRequirementsTool, ProvideFeedbackTool)
               Validates and provides feedback
    ▼
Return to Stage for HITL confirmation
```

### 3. HITL Content Review Flow

```
Stage generates artifact (e.g., prd.md)
    │
    ▼
InteractiveBackend::request_input()
    │ Options: [Pass, View Artifact, Provide Feedback, Cancel]
    │
    ├─► Pass → Continue to next stage
    │
    ├─► View Artifact → Open in editor, loop back
    │
    ├─► Provide Feedback → Store feedback, re-execute stage
    │                      Max loops: 5
    │
    └─► Cancel → Pause iteration, return error
```

### 4. Evolution Iteration Flow

```
User Request for Evolution
    │
    ▼
IterationExecutor::create_evolution_iteration()
    │ base_iteration_id: previous iteration
    │ inheritance: Full | Partial | None
    ▼
IterationExecutor::execute()
    │
    ├─► workspace::prepare_workspace()
    │   │ Copies files from base iteration based on inheritance mode
    │   │ - Full: Copy all artifacts + workspace
    │   │ - Partial: Copy artifacts only
    │   │ - None: Fresh workspace
    │   ▼
    │
    └─► knowledge::inject_project_knowledge()
        │ Loads base iteration's knowledge
        │ Injects into current iteration's memory
        ▼
    Determine start stage from inheritance mode
    Execute stages from start stage
```

### 5. PM Agent Post-Delivery Interaction

```
Iteration Completed
    │
    ▼
User sends message to PM Agent
    │
    ▼
execute_pm_agent_message_streaming()
    │ Location: crates/cowork-core/src/agents/mod.rs:559
    │ Loads project context, artifacts, memory
    ▼
create_project_manager_agent()
    │ Tools: PMGotoStageTool, PMCreateIterationTool,
    │        PMRespondTool, PMSaveDecisionTool, QueryMemoryTool
    ▼
Intent Recognition
    │
    ├─► Bug fix → PMGotoStageTool → Jump to Coding stage
    │
    ├─► New feature → PMCreateIterationTool → Create evolution iteration
    │
    └─► Question → PMRespondTool → Answer from memory/artifacts
```

