## QUICK NAVIGATION BY TASK

### "I need to modify the pipeline execution logic"
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/executor/mod.rs`

### "I need to add a new stage"
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/stages/` + `mod.rs` (register)

### "I need to add a new tool"
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/tools/` + `mod.rs` (re-export)

### "I need to modify HITL behavior"
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/interaction/mod.rs` (trait)
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/pipeline/executor/interaction_ext.rs` (flow)

### "I need to add a new agent instruction"
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/instructions/`

### "I need to modify storage format"
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/persistence/`
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/domain/` (entity changes)

### "I need to add external agent support"
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/acp/`
→ `crates/cowork-core/src/agents/external_coding_agent.rs`

### "I need to add a new CLI command"
→ `crates/cowork-cli/src/commands/`
→ `crates/cowork-cli/src/main.rs` (register)

### "I need to modify GUI backend"
→ `crates/cowork-gui/src-tauri/src/`

### "I need to modify GUI frontend"
→ `crates/cowork-gui/src/`
